The paper focuses on the intersection of AI and user experience design, specifically in the context of explainable AI. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). The paper also discusses algorithmic work on XAI, which suggests a potential fit with cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper touches on issues related to privacy and security, which could place it in cs.CY (Cryptography and Security). The use of a question bank to probe user needs aligns with research in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG).
